### ── REPORTING SERVICE (/reporting) ────────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Reports work against seed data — no additional setup required.

### 1. Sales dashboard — summary across all branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getSalesDashboard()
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 2. Branch performance — München
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getBranchPerformance(branchId='aaa00000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001')
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 3. Branch performance — all branches (branchId empty)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getBranchPerformance(branchId=null)
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 4. Conversion rates — direct sales funnel
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getConversionRates(funnelType='direct')
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 5. Conversion rates — reservation-led funnel
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getConversionRates(funnelType='reservation-led')
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 6. Vehicle sales report — entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/VehicleSalesReport
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 7. Reservation report — entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/ReservationReport
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 8. Offer conversion report — entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/OfferConversionReport
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 9. Branch performance report — entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/BranchPerformanceReport
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

### 10. Reporting as Customer — should be rejected (Manager/Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reporting/getSalesDashboard()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
